{"tid":1863427,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"裁判官吳重儀一度質疑稱：「我知道嚟做咩？我又唔係監警會。」","createTime":"2020-02-05T06:49:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T02:08:14.000Z","uid":77937,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1637ba644609f3dc50d92b2bd93e69c733518646","tid":1863427,"uid":77937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T06:49:07.000Z","msg":"辯方在庭上投訴指，警方拘捕時使用過分武力；其後將被告帶返警署後，再有七名便衣警員用黑布袋及黑膠袋將陳包裹起來，然後「由頭打到腳」。事後再有警員恐嚇他稱：「唔好作出投訴，唔好搵律師，除非以後你唔再出嚟，否則一定搵到你！」<br />\n<br />\n不過，辯方投訴期間，裁判官吳重儀一度質疑稱：「我知道嚟做咩？我又唔係監警會。」辯方解釋，有關投訴對日後審訊有重要影響，吳官聞言後批准辯方繼續陳詞。<br />\nSource: Apple Daily<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/3be7w44\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3be7w44&d=%2FE8yPsxO6SBEJdrny20pcVDApO%2Br9QW7Zx2priNtVuo%3D&h=bdf1ead1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/3be7w44</a>"},{"pid":"564002c8b0fc7b3941d1acdfd12b6bedad9e0806","tid":1863427,"uid":77937,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T06:49:20.000Z","msg":"裁判官吳重儀"},{"pid":"f803acbbdc2988e50c855394299c01eab11e3b47","tid":1863427,"uid":77937,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T06:49:33.000Z","msg":"裁判官吳重儀"},{"pid":"67a5c6b376897915375f7fa35d932d09169e6631","tid":1863427,"uid":77937,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T06:49:48.000Z","msg":"裁判官吳重儀"},{"pid":"8fc11444ff73c013311a08a466350e1b081f3393","tid":1863427,"uid":77937,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T06:50:02.000Z","msg":"裁判官吳重儀"},{"pid":"74fae83be111ec0a65cb9cbb5347c58fed1185ad","tid":1863427,"uid":77937,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T06:51:50.000Z","msg":"裁判官吳重儀"},{"pid":"e8c4fc3bf73ae7679fd00812e933e72a5fdac500","tid":1863427,"uid":247032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T06:52:27.000Z","msg":"推<br />\ndead body同公文袋出黎未"},{"pid":"48890711a17a51296f6cf43404eab151ab43795d","tid":1863427,"uid":199332,"like":0,"di